des:
This skill will give you the real-time Bitcoin Price on Coinbase.

The data is directly pulled from Coinbase server and you will know the real Bitcoin price on Coinbase.


How to use 'Bitcoin Price on Coinbase | Real-time Price'?

You don't need to open your Computer or unlock your phone anymore. Just say 'Alexa, open Bitcoin Price on Coinbase' and you'll get the latest price.
